Summary: It looked like it could of been a UFO plane or something. Never landed but desapeared into woods.u
divs: Sighting DetailsI was in the car on my way to school wen I noticed a big blue light floating feet away from me, my mom said it was a UFO plane. It made sence, it looked like it was. I was too in shock to take a picture and by the time I was gonna take it, it desapeared into the woods. But my mom claims to seen more like it in them woofs.
